(187, 52, 'root', '2022-05-25 09:45:50', 0, 3, 1, 9, 0, 'where-is-5g-technology-used', '', '', 'Where is 5G Technology Used?', 3, 'blog/5g-technology-used.jpg', '', '<p>The letter &quot;G&quot; in the term 5G stands for &quot;generation&quot; in English. In the simplest terms, downloading 500 MB of data in 5G technology is completed in one second. It is 20 times faster than the 4.5 G technology used today. &quot;5G&quot; also means that this technology infrastructure has developed for the 5th time.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What are the Advantages of 5G Technology?</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>5G technology</strong> is a term that sums up the fast age of the internet. With the fastest internet available, users also have the opportunity to download 4K videos with very high image quality in just minutes. In addition, <strong>5G technology</strong> is also very innovative, thanks to its wireless nature. No cable infrastructure is required in 5G. Users obtain the Internet from signals in the air, just like the Internet of mobile phones. 5G makes phone calls over the Internet and browsing websites faster. In particular, data uploaded or downloaded from the internet is downloaded to the phone/computer or smart devices in a faster and shorter time.</p>\n\n<p><strong>When Will 5G Come to Turkey?</strong></p>\n\n<p>There is no definite date for when <strong>5G technology</strong> will be used in Turkey. However, it will be implemented first in the United States. In Turkey, 4.5 G technology currently in use. This technology is used by 51 million people. The large number of users is of great importance in terms of the necessity of moving simultaneously with the world in the field of technology. Therefore, it will not take a long time for this technology to come to our country.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What are the Uses of 5G?</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>5G technology</strong> is not just about getting fast data from the internet or uploading data fast to the internet. The usage areas of 5G will spread to a very widespread environment. It will support the development of many areas, especially automation. At the same time, 5G will be used extensively in homes and workplaces. Apart from this subject; 5G is currently used in business development centers in various parts of the world for use in the healthcare field. Studies to obtain more data from the babies in the incubator will be used in areas such as the rehabilitation of paralyzed people, and will be the basis of medical development.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://refine-tr.com/\">https://refine-tr.com/</a></p>\n\n<p>Lanner Electronics:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lannerinc.com/\">https://www.lannerinc.com</a></p>\n', 'The letter \"G\" in the term 5G stands for \"generation\" in English.', NULL),
(188, 51, 'root', '2022-05-25 09:46:05', 0, 1, 1, 10, 0, 'importance-of-network-devices', '', '', 'Importance of Network Devices', 3, 'blog/importance-network-devices.jpg', '', '<p>Network allows users to share hardware and software resources in computer systems. In order to use network devices, it is also necessary to establish a network infrastructure. Information, software, files, applications and hardware can be shared via the network. Besides that, the central control of the devices such as network printers and network cameras etc. is also provided securely. Network devices is also preferred for storage, backup and VoIP systems (IP phone) as well as these features. Network has reached a further point thanks to the widespread use of concepts and technologies such as &quot;internet of things, smart home systems&quot;. In the past, networking required a lot of equipment along with technical knowledge. Network setup was very cumbersome. But today, devices are automatically connected to each other over the network. In this way, it is much easier for devices to recognize each other. The main devices required to create a network are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Hub</li>\n	<li>Switch</li>\n	<li>Repeater</li>\n	<li>Bridge</li>\n	<li>Router</li>\n	<li>Firewall Devices (Firewall)</li>\n	<li>Access Point</li>\n	<li>NIC (Network Interface Card)</li>\n	<li>Modem</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>How is Network Security Provided?</h2>\n\n<p>The development of network structure and devices, especially their use in every field, brought the issue of network security to the fore. Malicious software that only affected computers in the past, puts many systems at risk due to the fact that devices and systems are so intertwined today. You must ensure network security so that the devices connected to your network are not damaged by these threats. The security methods you should use on each device are different. The security methods you can use according to your network devices are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Firewall</li>\n	<li>VPN (Virtual Private Networks)</li>\n	<li>Antivirus</li>\n	<li>IDS (Intrusion Detection Systems)</li>\n	<li>URL Filtering (Web Filtering)</li>\n	<li>Strong Authentication</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://refine-tr.com/\">https://refine-tr.com/</a></p>\n\n<p>Lanner Electronics:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.lannerinc.com/\">https://www.lannerinc.com</a></p>\n', 'Network allows users to share hardware and software resources in computer systems.', NULL),
