(111, 4, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-05-12 13:32:55', 0, 1, 0, 45, 0, 'nca-1513', '', '', 'NCA-1513', 'Desktop Network Appliance Powered by Intel® Atom® C3000 (Denverton) CPU', 'pdf/sample.pdf', 'pdf/sample.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>Intel&reg; Atom&reg; C3000 Processor (Codenamed Denverton)</li>\n	<li>6x or 4x GbE RJ45 or 4x GbE RJ45 + 2x SFP (by SKU)</li>\n	<li>DDR4 2133/1866MHz, Max. 16GB</li>\n	<li>1x RJ45 Console, 2x USB 3.0/2.0, Onboard EMMC 8G, 1x Nano SIM for M.2</li>\n	<li>1x Mini-PCIe, 1x M.2 2280/2242, 1x M.2 3042&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n', 'The NCA-1513, a desktop network appliance powered by Intel® Atom® C3558/C3338/C3308 CPU, features robust performance and Intel QAT, greatly boosting network responsiveness and security by distributing processing power to more critical applications and by offloading computationally intensive compression and encryption/decryption tasks.', '	Intel® Atom® C3000 (Denverton)', 'SoC', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'DDR4 2133/1866 MHz ECC/Non-ECC SODIMM (By SKU)', '16 GB', '1 x 260-pin SODIMM', '1 x 2.5” Bay (Optional) 1 x EMMC 8GB', '6x GbE RJ45 Intel® i211 (By SKU)', '2 Pair of Gen3 (by SKU)', '1 x RJ45', '', '', 'TPM 2.0', '1 x DC Jack', '40W Power Adapter', '1 x Mini-PCIe (PCIe/USB2.0) 1 x M.2 2280/2242 (SATA3.0) 1x M.2 3042 (USB3.0)', '1 * Reset Button', '1 x Cooling Fan w/ Smart Fan', 'RoHS, CE/FCC Class B, UL', '-20°C to 70°C', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 95% (non-condensing)', '231 mm x 44 mm x 200 mm (9.09\" x 1.73\" x 7.87\")', '1.2 kg (2.64 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 15, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(112, 25, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-05-12 13:33:36', 0, 1, 0, 35, 0, 'fw-8894', '', '', 'FW-8894', '1U High Performance x86 Network Appliance for Enterprise Firewall, UTM and IPS.\n', '', '', '<ul>\n	<li>Dual CPU Sockets for Intel&reg; E5-2600 v3/v4 (Haswell/Broadwell-EP) with Wellsburg PCH</li>\n	<li>4 NIC module slots up to 32 LAN ports</li>\n	<li>Support for Intel&reg; 1G/10G/40G network controllers</li>\n	<li>Up to 25 Gbps QuickAssist crypto acceleration by Intel&reg; DH8925</li>\n	<li>Supports DDR4 2133 MHz memory up to 512 GB</li>\n	<li>1+1 ATX redundant powers 650W</li>\n	<li>Optional TPM support</li>\n	<li>OPMA slot for IPMI</li>\n	<li>4 hot-swappable cooling fans with smart fan control</li>\n</ul>\n', 'The FW-8894 is a high performance 1U rackmount network security system built with Intel’s latest Haswell/Broadwell-EP CPU and Intel® C612 Wellsburg PCH (codenamed “Grantley”), offering comparative advantages at providing additional processor improvement, faster packet processing performance, higher memory bandwidth and more power efficiency.\n\nThe FW-8894 features two Intel® Xeon E5-2600 v3/v4 Series processors for handling not only enterprise-grade network traffic data rates but also associated control/signaling infrastructure requirements. Also notable is the support for hardware-based Intel® QuickAssist acceleration technology, enabling offloading encryption/decryption and compression for up to 25 Gbps.\n\nThe FW-8894’s modular interface allows the installation of various Lanner modules, making it available to a maximum of four slots for 1G, 10G, or 40G, Fiber or Copper/Bypass NIC modules.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 14, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
