(181, 18, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-05-13 13:26:57', 0, 1, 1, 41, 0, 'fw-8896', '', '', 'FW-8896', 'High-performance x86 Network Security Appliance based on Dual Intel Xeon E5-2600 v3 CPUs.\n\n', '', '', '<ul>\n	<li>Dual CPU Sockets for Intel Xeon E5-2600 v3/v4 (Haswell/Broadwell-EP) with C612 chipset</li>\n	<li>Low-powered DDR4 2133 MHz (Max. 512 GB)</li>\n	<li>8 NIC module slots (up to 64 GbE ports)</li>\n	<li>FW-8896A/C/E/G with Coleto Creek 8925 acceleration chip</li>\n	<li>1+1 ATX 600W/800W redundant power</li>\n	<li>1x PCI-E x8 expansion</li>\n	<li>OPMA slot for IPMI</li>\n	<li>Gen. 2 or Gen. 3 LAN bypass function</li>\n	<li>Support N+1 hot-swappable cooling fans with smart fan control</li>\n</ul>\n', 'The FW-8896 is the successor to Lanner’s DPDK-ready flagship network computing platform and is powered by two Intel® Xeon® processor E5-2600 v3/v4 (codenamed Haswell/Broadwell-EP) and the Intel® C612 series chipset (codenamed Wellsburg), featuring 22nm process, DDR4 support and enhanced SATA support. The new generation of Intel® Xeon® E5-2600 v3 processors greatly improve hardware performance, bandwidth, CPU and power efficiency, making appliances such as the FW-8896 ideal solutions for tasks that require optimized instructions for communications workloads and enhanced packet processing capabilities, such as high-performance network security, enterprise firewall, UTM, IPS, application delivery controller and WAN optimization. The FW-8896 is equipped with 8 NIC modules, capable of supporting up to 64 GbE ports; also notable is that a maximum of sixteen quad-channel 2133 MHz DDR4 can be accommodated, providing up to 512GB of memory capacity.\n', '1x LGA1151', 'Intel® C246/Q370/H310', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'DDR4 up to 2666 UDIMM 8/16GB ; ECC DIMM 8/16GB (SKU A Only)', '32 GB', '2 x 288-pin DIMM', '', '', '3 Pairs Gen3', '1 x RJ45', 'From Mini-PCIe Slot (Optional)', '2 x USB 3.0', 'Yes (Optional)', 'AC Power Inlet on PSU', '220W ATX Single PSU', '1x PCIe*8 FH/HL (Optional), 1x Mini-PCIe (PCIe/USB2.0)', '1', '3 x or 2 x Cooling Fans with Smart Fan', 'RoHS, CE/FCC Class A, UL', '0~40ºC Operating', '-20~70ºC Non-Operating', '5~90% Operating', '540 x 500 x 230 mm', '8.5 kg', 'Yes', 'Yes', 14, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
