(443, 63, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-05-17 10:16:53', 0, 1, 1, -1, 0, 'pgn-300', '', '', 'PGN-300', 'Swappable 4G LTE CAT-6 Radio Modem for Mission-Critical Communications\n', 'pdf/PGN-300-datasheet.pdf', '', '<ul>\n	<li>4G LTE CAT-6 Radio Modem Compatible for Lanner Vehicle PC, Industrial PC and Network Appliances</li>\n	<li>PTCRB and AT&amp;T Certification Ready</li>\n	<li>2x SIM Card Readers, 2x 4G LTE Antenna</li>\n	<li>SATA connector with USB 3.0 signal and Hot Swappable Capability</li>\n	<li>4G LTE Failover for Business Continuity</li>\n	<li>Designed for Network Failover, Surveillance and Vehicle Applications</li>\n	<li>Swappable Caddy</li>\n	<li>System Compatibility: V3S,V6S,LEC-2290,NCR-1510D/E/F,FW-7573B</li>\n</ul>\n', 'Lanner’s PGN-300 is a 4G LTE modem card compatible with Lanner Vehicle PC, Industrial PC and Network Appliances. The scalable modem card enables Lanner platform with 4G LTE Connectivity. This LTE modem card is PTCRB and AT&T certification ready, Verizon is under certification process. PGN-300 is built-in with 4G LTE Radio Modem with LTE Cat-6 embedded module, and provides dual SIM card readers and dual 4G LTE Antenna inputs. The PCIe 3.0 connector interface is hot-swappable. To assure connectivity, PGN-300 offers 4G LTE failure for 24/7 operating continuity. The modem card is optimally designed for video surveillance and in-vehicle computing.\n\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 8, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(444, 9, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-05-18 11:09:21', 0, 1, 1, 56, 0, 'nca-1510', '', '', 'NCA-1510', 'Fanless SFF Desktop Network Security Appliance for SME Edge Security ', 'pdf/NCA-1510.pdf', 'pdf/NCA-1510_User_Manual.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>Intel&reg; Atom&trade; 2 ~8 Cores C3758, C3558 or C3308 CPU (Codenamed Denverton)</li>\n	<li>4x RJ45, 2x SFP or 2x RJ45 (By SKU), 1 pairs Gen3 (By SKU)</li>\n	<li>1x 260-pin DDR4 2133/2400MHz ECC DIMM, Max. 8GB</li>\n	<li>Intel&reg; QuickAssist Technology at 10Gbps</li>\n	<li>Intel&reg; AES-NI &amp; TPM Support</li>\n	<li>1x Mini USB Console, 2x USB 3.0</li>\n	<li>1x Mini-PCIe, 1x M.2, 1x Nano SIM Accessibility</li>\n	<li>1x 2.5&rdquo; HDD/SSD Bay, 1x Onboard EMMC 8GB</li>\n	<li>Fanless Design</li>\n</ul>\n', 'Powered by Intel® Atom® C3000 (codenamed Denverton) CPU, the NCA-1510 features robust performance and Intel’s QuickAssist Technology, offering cryptographic acceleration and commercial-grade LAN functions in a 231mm x 200mm x 44mm form factor. It is the ideal fanless SFF desktop network security appliance for managing edge security at small and medium enterprises.', 'Intel® Atom® C3000 Series 2~8 Cores (Denverton)', 'SoC', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'DDR4 2133MHz ECC DIMM', '8 GB', '1 x 260-pin SODIMM', '1 x EMMC 8GB', '', '1 Pair of Gen3 (by SKU)', '1 x Mini USB', '', '', '', '1 x DC Jack', '36W or 60W Power Adapter (By SKU)', '', '', 'Fanless', 'RoHS, CE/FCC Class B, UL', '-20°C to 70°C', '0°C to 50°C', '5% to 95% (non-condensing)', '217 mm x 44 mm x 145.5 mm (8.54', '1.2 kg (2.64 lbs)', 'Yes ', 'Yes', 15, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
