(1126, 1, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-17 14:30:14', 0, 1, 1, 43, 0, 'nci-200', '', '', 'NCI-200', 'Fanless x86 Desktop Network Appliance with Wide Operating Temperature', 'pdf/NCI-200.pdf', 'pdf/sample.pdf', '<ul class=\"mt-5\">\n	<li>Intel&reg; Atom&trade; processor C2308/C2508 (Codenamed &ldquo;Rangeley&rdquo;)</li>\n	<li>Onboard 4 x GbE RJ45, 2 x GbE SFP (SKU A)</li>\n	<li>Support Intel QuickAssist crypto acceleration</li>\n	<li>Wide operating temperature -20~55&ordm;C</li>\n	<li>Support 2 pairs of Gen.3 LAN bypass</li>\n	<li>1.5KV magnetic isolation protection</li>\n	<li>4KV ESD protection</li>\n	<li>1 x DB-9 for serial management, 1 x optional DB-9 serial port</li>\n	<li>2 x internal PCIe x1 slots for expansion</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', 'The NCA-1031, powered by the Intel® Atom® N4200/N3350 (Apollo Lake) processor, is a desktop form factor network appliance designed for entry-level network security, gateway or vCPE.', 'Intel® Atom™ processor C2308/C2508 (Codenamed “Rangeley”)', 'SoC', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'Single Channel DDR3 1333 MHz, 1.5 V, ECC', '8 GB', '1 x 204-pin SODIMM', '1 x 2.5” SSD bay (SSD is not included)', '', '2 pairs Gen.3', '', '', '', '', '12~48 Vdc (adaptor excluded)', 'Phoenix contact 4-pin connector with lock', '2 x PCIe x1 (Internal)', '', 'Fanless design with corrugated aluminum', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A, RoHS', '-40°C to 70°C', '-20°C to 55°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '230 mm x 65 mm x 170 mm (9.06', '2 kg (4.4 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 15, 'products/nci-200.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '4 x RJ-45, 2 x SFP (SKU A)', '', '4 x Intel 1 GbE with Marvell PHY', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1.5 KV Built-in', '', '', '', 'Passive CPU heatsink', '4KV for all signals contacted', '1 x DB-9 for serial management + 1 optional DB-9', '', '2 x Type A', '', '', '', '', 'Linux Kernel 2.6 or above', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '',