(1164, 6, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-20 08:23:18', 0, 3, 1, 46, 0, 'nca-1010', '', '', 'NCA-1010', 'Compact Fanless x86 Network Appliance with Intel Bay Trail Platform (Atom E3800 CPU)\n', 'pdf/NCA-1010.pdf', 'pdf/NCA-1010_User_Manual.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>Compact form factor</li>\n	<li>Intel Atom E3815 or E3825 CPU (codename Bay Trail)</li>\n	<li>1 x DDR3L SODIMM memory up to 8GB</li>\n	<li>Fanless design</li>\n	<li>Built-in security engine: hardware assisted AES-NI</li>\n	<li>3 x RJ45 GbE LAN ports, 1 x USB 3.0, 1 x USB 2.0, 1 x HDMI port</li>\n	<li>1 x full-length mini-PCIe slot for Wi-Fi/BT/3G connectivity</li>\n	<li>1 x half-length mini-PCIe slot for mSATA</li>\n	<li>1 x antenna hole</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', 'NCA-1010 is Lanner’s revolutionary ultra compact x86 networking system built with Intel® Bay Trail CPU (Atom™ E3815/E3825). The central processor comes with hardware-assisted security mechanisms including AES-NI, allowing only authorized software or data to run on NCA-1010. With built-in instruction commands, NCA-1010 helps manage and secure devices connected to local WiFi network, like a compact entry-level firewall or multi-service gateway.\nDespite its compact size, NCA-1010 delivers rich I/O connectivity and scalability. In terms of scalability, NCA-1010 comes with one HDMI port for high definition display, one console port for device network management, three LAN ports for network connections, two USB ports (one in USB 2.0 and another in USB 3.0 specifications) for external devices, and one antenna hole for signal reception. The rich I/O connectivity makes NCA-1010 a widely deployable system in small area network environments.', 'Intel® Bay Trail E3815 or E3825 CPU', 'N/A', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'DDR3L 1067 MHz non-ECC', '8 GB', '1 x 204-pin SODIMM', '1 x mSATA mini (half size)', '', 'N/A', '1 x RJ45', 'HDMI port x 1', '', '', '', '', '1 x Mini-PCIe', '1 x reset button, hardware reset only', 'Fanless', 'CE Class B, FCC Class B, RoHS', '-20°C to 70°C', '0°C to 40°C', '', '124.26 mm x 19.4 mm x 119.66 mm (4.89', '0.5 kg (1.1 lbs)', '', 'Yes', 15, 'products/NCA-1010_back.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3 x RJ-45', '', '3 x Intel i211', '', '', '', '', 'N/A', '', '', '', '', '', 'Passive CPU heatsink', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Windows 7, Windows 8, WES 7, WES 8, Linux (Fedora 18/Yocto)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
