(1292, 28, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-21 12:55:30', 0, 3, 1, 32, 0, 'fw-8771', '', '', 'FW-8771', 'Rackmount x86 Network Security Platform based on Intel® Xeon® E3-1200 v3 processor (Haswell).\n', 'pdf/FW-8771.pdf', 'pdf/FW-8771_User_Manual.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>Support Intel&reg; Xeon&reg; E3-1200 v3 processor</li>\n	<li>Compact Rackmount 1U with Shorter Depth Design</li>\n	<li>LAN Bypass</li>\n	<li>Expandable with Lanner Ethernet Modules (FW-8771C only)</li>\n	<li>IPMI/Management port</li>\n	<li>ECC Memory Support</li>\n	<li>Redundant Power Supply Units (FW-8771C only)</li>\n	<li>Watchdog</li>\n	<li>2 x USB 3.0</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', "The FW-8771 is a 1U rackmountable network security platform incorporating Intel\'s latest Xeon® Haswell CPU.\nBased on the new Intel® 22nm process architecture, the proccessor improves CPU performance and efficiency in power consumption. The Intel® AES New Instruction (AES-NI) enhancements use hardware-based acceleration to encrypt/decrypt the data. The improvements in processing performance is over 10% compared with the previous generation Ivy Bridge. This allows network appliances to operate at ultra-high speed.", 'Support Intel® Xeon® E3-1275/1225 v3 CPU (Haswell', 'Intel C226 Chipset (Lynx Point PCH)', 'AMI BIOS 64 Mb', 'DDR3 1600 MHz DIMM with ECC support', '32 GB', '4 x 240-pin DIMM', '2 x 2.5” HDD kit', '', '3 pairs of 3rd Generation LAN bypass', '1 x RJ-45', '1 x VGA (optional)', '', '', '', '', '2 x PCIe*8 for NIC (Optional Rear PCIE)', '', '3 cooling fans', 'CE Emission, FCC Class A, RoHS', '-20°C to 70°C', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing', '431 mm x 44 mm x 468 mm (16.97', '7 kg (15.4 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 14, 'products/FW-8771_front.png', '', '', '', '', '', '1 x CFast', '', '', '', '8 x GbE RJ45 ports', '', '8 x Intel i210', '2 (FW-8771C only)', '', '', '', 'By Project', '', '', '1, shared with IPMI port', '', '', 'Passive heatsink', '', '', '', '2 x Type A', '', '', '270W Single Power Supply or Redundant 300W PSUs', '', 'Windows 7,8,2000, XP, Vista, Server 2008, 2012, Linux Kernel 2.6 or above', '', '', '', '', '', '2 x 20 characters (optional)', '', '', '5% to 95% (non-condensing)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
