(1335, 37, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-22 09:08:43', 0, 3, 1, 23, 0, 'htca-6600', '', '', 'HTCA-6600', 'High Availability Chassis 6U Telecom Network Appliance with 6 x86 CPU Blades and 6 I/O Blades\n', 'pdf/HTCA-6600.pdf', 'pdf/HTCA-6600_User_Manual.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>High availability, full redundancy and extreme high performance</li>\n	<li>6 CPU blades in the rear, per blade supports up to 2 Intel&reg; Xeon&reg; E5-2600 v3/v4 CPUs and 16x DDR4</li>\n	<li>BCM StrataXGS&trade; Trident-II/II+ BCM56854/56860 Switch Fabric with 720/1280 Gbps</li>\n	<li>6 x Swappable I/O blades on the front, supporting up to 2x Switch blades or 6x Ethernet blades</li>\n	<li>NEBS compliant design</li>\n	<li>Redundant power supply and removable fan module</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', 'HTCA-6600 is designed in 6U, with six CPU blades and a combination of six Ethernet NI/switch blade slots. While sharing the same CPU and memory configurations as HTCA-6200, two Intel® Xeon® E5-2600 v3/v4 CPUs and sixteen DDR4 R-DIMM sockets for each blade as stated above, HTCA-6600 comes with six front-cabling, swappable Ethernet NI/switch blades. The top 2 blade slots are reserved for switch or Ethernet NI blades, while the other four slots are solely used for Ethernet NI blades. The Ethernet NI blade comes with the same configuration as HTCA-6200, which delivers thirty-two 10GbE ports. As the higher-end model, HTCA-6600 is designed with switch blade and CPU blade redundancy. In case one of the blades is encountered with failure, the other will take all the work loads.', 'Intel® Xeon® processor E5-2600 v3/v4 Series', 'Intel C612 Chipset', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'Quad-channel DDR4 2400MHz (Registered)', '512GB (Registered) per M/B tray', 'Up to 16 x 288-pin DIMM per M/B tray Switch Blade', '6 x 3.5” swappable drive bays,', '', '', '1 x RJ45', '', '', '', 'AC 85~264V DC -36~-72V', 'AC 1200 watt N+1 Redundant /each DC 1010 watt N+1 Redundant /each PM bus support, up to 5 PSU slots', '', '', '5 x hot-swappable cooling fan sets with smart fan control for each computing blade', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A', '-20°C to 70°C', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '438 mm x 265.9 mm x 685.8 mm (17.24\" x 10.47\" x 27.00\")', '55 kg (121 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 19, 'products/HTCA-6600_Front_2021.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Up to 32 x SFP+', '', 'XL710', '', '', '', '', 'OPMA socket to support IPMI (IAC-AST2300)', '', '', '', '', '', 'CPU heatsinks with fan duct', '', '', '', '1 x Type A', '', '', '', '', 'Linux Cent OS 7.2 or above', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(1339, 40, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-22 10:14:22', 0, 1, 0, 22, 0, 'hcp-72i2', '', '', 'HCP-72i2', '2 X86 CPU Bıçaklı ve 3 G / Ç Bıçaklı Yüksek Kullanılabilirlik Rafa Monte 2U Telekom Ağ Cihazı.', 'pdf/HCP-72i2.pdf', '', '<ul>\n	<li>Y&uuml;ksek kullanılabilirlik, tam yedeklilik ve aşırı y&uuml;ksek performans</li>\n	<li>Arkada 2 CPU kanadı var. 4 Adede kadar Intel&reg; Xeon&reg; E5-2690 v3 CPU ve 32x DDR4 RDIMM desteği</li>\n	<li>NTB portu &uuml;zerinden &ccedil;ift anakart iletişimi</li>\n	<li>&ouml;n tarafta 3 adet değiştirilebilir G / &Ccedil; kanadı. Bir dizide 36 x 1gbe&#39;ye veya 24 x 10gbe&#39;ye kadar ağ bağlantı noktasını destekleyin</li>\n	<li>2 x değiştirilebilir 2,5 &quot;HDD yuvası</li>\n	<li>NEBS uyumluluğu</li>\n	<li>Yedekli g&uuml;&ccedil; kaynağı ve &ccedil;ıkarılabilir fan mod&uuml;l&uuml;</li>\n	<li>Uzaktan y&ouml;netim i&ccedil;in IPMI bağlantı noktası</li>\n	<li>Kolay teşhis ve yapılandırma i&ccedil;in menteşe LCD mod&uuml;l&uuml;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', 'HCP-72ı2, taşıyıcı sınıfı ağ kontrolü, bulut bilişim ve veri merkezi için zorlu gereksinimleri karşılamak üzere oluşturulan Lanner\'ın benzersiz Hibrit Telekomünikasyon Bilgi İşlem Mimarisi (HybrıdTCA ™) ile oluşturulmuş 2U raf montajlı bir telekom ağ cihazıdır. HCP-72 ı2, kontrol, yönetim ve veri işlemeyi tek bir sistemde bütünleştirir ve donanım tasarımı, özelleştirme seçenekleri ve maliyet / enerji verimliliği açısından yaygın gelişmiş TCA altyapısına göre avantajlara sahiptir. İki x86 anakartla birlikte gelir ve her biri LGA2011-3\'te iki Intel Xeon E5-2600 v3 serisi işlemciyi (Haswell-EP) destekler. HCP-72ı2, üç (maks.) bir dizi SFP veya bakır kombinasyonunda 36 adede kadar 1GbE ağ bağlantı noktasına veya 24 adede kadar 10GbE ağ bağlantı noktasına sahip değiştirilebilir G / Ç kanatları. Bu özel cihaz aynı zamanda 32 adet dört kanallı DDR4 DIMM soketi ve 2 adet çıkarılabilir SAS / SATA HDD yuvası ile birlikte gelir ve genişleme ihtiyaçlarının çoğunu geleceğe karşı korur.', '4 x Intel® Xeon® processor E5-2690 v3 series (Haswell-EP)', 'Intel C612 Chipset', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'Quad-channel DDR4 2133 MHz (Registered)', '512GB (Registered)', 'Up to 32 x 240-pin DIMM', '2 x 2.5” swappable drive bays, 2 x mSATA sockets', '', '', 'Up to 2 x RJ45; each blade x 1', '', '', '', 'AC 100~240V@50~60Hz DC -36~-72V', 'AC 1200 watt 1+1 Redundant /each DC 1010 watt 1+ Redundant /each PM bus support', '', 'Yes', 'Up to 10 x independent hot-swappable cooling Fans with smart fan control, each blade x 5', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A', '', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '431 mm x 88 mm x 718.1 mm (16.97', '35 kg (77 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 19, 'products/HCP-72i2.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'RJ-45 ,SFP, SFP+', '', 'Intel 82574L & 82599ES', '', '', '', '', 'OPMA socket to support IPMI (IAC-AST2300)', '', '', '', '', '', 'Up to 4 x CPU heatsinks with fan duct; each blade x 2', '', '', '', '2 x Type A', '', '', '', '', 'Linux Kernel 2.6 or above', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hinge LCM', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(1340, 40, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-22 10:16:46', 0, 1, 1, 22, 0, 'hcp-72i2', '', '', 'HCP-72i2', 'High Availability Rackmount 2U Telecom Network Appliance with 2 x86 CPU Blades and 3 I/O Blades\n', 'pdf/HCP-72i2.pdf', '', '<ul>\n	<li>High availability, full redundancy and extreme high performance</li>\n	<li>2 CPU blades in the rear. Support up to 4 Intel&reg; Xeon&reg; E5-2690 v3 CPUs and 32x DDR4 R-DIMM</li>\n	<li>Dual mainboard communication through NTB port</li>\n	<li>3 swappable I/O blades on the front. Support up to 36 x 1GbE or 24 x 10GbE network ports in an array</li>\n	<li>2 x swappable 2.5&quot; HDD bay</li>\n	<li>NEBS compliance</li>\n	<li>Redundant power supply and removable fan module</li>\n	<li>IPMI port for remote management</li>\n	<li>Hinge LCD module for easy diagnostics and configuration</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', "The HCP-72i2 is a 2U rackmount telecom network appliance built with Lanner\'s unique Hybrid Telecommunications Computing Architecture (HybridTCA™) ,which is created to meet the challenging requirements for carrier-grade network control, cloud computing and data center.\n\nThe HCP-72i2 integrates control, management and data processing in one system and has advantages over the prevalent AdvancedTCA infrastructure in aspects of hardware design, customization options and cost/energy efficiency. It comes with two x86 mainboards and each supports two Intel Xeon E5-2600 v3 series processors (Haswell-EP) on LGA2011-3.\n\nThe HCP-72i2 can be fitted, via the three (max.) swappable I/O blades, with up to 36 1GbE network ports or 24 10GbE network ports in an array of SFP or copper combinations. This particular appliance also comes with 32 quad-channel DDR4 DIMM sockets and 2 removable SAS/SATA HDD bays, future-proofing most of the expansion needs.", '4 x Intel® Xeon® processor E5-2690 v3 series (Haswell-EP)', 'Intel C612 Chipset', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'Quad-channel DDR4 2133 MHz (Registered)', '512GB (Registered)', 'Up to 32 x 240-pin DIMM', '2 x 2.5” swappable drive bays, 2 x mSATA sockets', '', '', 'Up to 2 x RJ45; each blade x 1', '', '', '', 'AC 100~240V@50~60Hz DC -36~-72V', 'AC 1200 watt 1+1 Redundant /each DC 1010 watt 1+1 Redundant /each PM bus support', '', 'Yes', 'Up to 10 x independent hot-swappable cooling Fans with smart fan control, each blade x 5', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A', '', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '431 mm x 88 mm x 718.1 mm (16.97', '35 kg (77 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 19, 'products/HCP-72i2.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'RJ-45 ,SFP, SFP+', '', 'Intel 82574L & 82599ES', '', '', '', '', 'OPMA socket to support IPMI (IAC-AST2300)', '', '', '', '', '', 'Up to 4 x CPU heatsinks with fan duct; each blade x 2', '', '', '', '2 x Type A', '', '', '', '', 'Linux Kernel 2.6 or above', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hinge LCM', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
