(1344, 40, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-22 10:21:42', 0, 3, 1, 22, 0, 'hcp-72i2', '', '', 'HCP-72i2', 'High Availability Rackmount 2U Telecom Network Appliance with 2 x86 CPU Blades and 3 I/O Blades\n', 'pdf/HCP-72i2.pdf', '', '<ul>\n	<li>High availability, full redundancy and extreme high performance</li>\n	<li>2 CPU blades in the rear. Support up to 4 Intel&reg; Xeon&reg; E5-2690 v3 CPUs and 32x DDR4 R-DIMM</li>\n	<li>Dual mainboard communication through NTB port</li>\n	<li>3 swappable I/O blades on the front. Support up to 36 x 1GbE or 24 x 10GbE network ports in an array</li>\n	<li>2 x swappable 2.5&quot; HDD bay</li>\n	<li>NEBS compliance</li>\n	<li>Redundant power supply and removable fan module</li>\n	<li>IPMI port for remote management</li>\n	<li>Hinge LCD module for easy diagnostics and configuration</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', "The HCP-72i2 is a 2U rackmount telecom network appliance built with Lanner\'s unique Hybrid Telecommunications Computing Architecture (HybridTCA™) ,which is created to meet the challenging requirements for carrier-grade network control, cloud computing and data center.\n\nThe HCP-72i2 integrates control, management and data processing in one system and has advantages over the prevalent AdvancedTCA infrastructure in aspects of hardware design, customization options and cost/energy efficiency. It comes with two x86 mainboards and each supports two Intel Xeon E5-2600 v3 series processors (Haswell-EP) on LGA2011-3.\n\nThe HCP-72i2 can be fitted, via the three (max.) swappable I/O blades, with up to 36 1GbE network ports or 24 10GbE network ports in an array of SFP or copper combinations. This particular appliance also comes with 32 quad-channel DDR4 DIMM sockets and 2 removable SAS/SATA HDD bays, future-proofing most of the expansion needs.", '4 x Intel® Xeon® processor E5-2690 v3 series (Haswell-EP)', 'Intel C612 Chipset', 'AMI SPI Flash BIOS', 'Quad-channel DDR4 2133 MHz (Registered)', '512GB (Registered)', 'Up to 32 x 240-pin DIMM', '2 x 2.5” swappable drive bays, 2 x mSATA sockets', '', '', 'Up to 2 x RJ45; each blade x 1', '', '', '', 'AC 100~240V@50~60Hz DC -36~-72V', 'AC 1200 watt 1+1 Redundant /each DC 1010 watt 1+1 Redundant /each PM bus support', '', 'Yes', 'Up to 10 x independent hot-swappable cooling Fans with smart fan control, each blade x 5', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A', '', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '431 mm x 88 mm x 718.1 mm (16.97', '35 kg (77 lbs)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 19, 'products/HCP-72i2.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'RJ-45 ,SFP, SFP+', '', 'Intel 82574L & 82599ES', '', '', '', '', 'OPMA socket to support IPMI (IAC-AST2300)', '', '', '', '', '', 'Up to 4 x CPU heatsinks with fan duct; each blade x 2', '', '', '', '2 x Type A', '', '', '', '', 'Linux Kernel 2.6 or above', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hinge LCM', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
