(1409, 48, 'fikirbuzz', '2022-06-29 07:09:08', 0, 3, 1, 13, 0, 'hlm-1030', '', '', 'HLM-1030', '100 GbE Switch Blade with Broadcom StrataXGS Tomahawk BCM56960\n', 'pdf/HLM-1030.pdf', 'pdf/HLM-1030_User_Manual.pdf', '<ul>\n	<li>Fabric interface switch blade with 6x 100GbE QSFP28, 4x 40GbE QSFP+ and 16x 10GbE SFP+</li>\n	<li>Broadcom StrataXGS Tomahawk BCM56960 3.2Tbps bandwidth Multilayer Switch</li>\n	<li>Compatible with HTCA-6600 and HTCA-6200</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"accel-snackbar\" style=\"left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 0px); top: 50px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n', 'The HLM-1030 switch blade provides 6x 100GbE QSFP28, 4x 40GbE QSFP+ and 16x 10GbE SFP+ fabric interface. It use Broadcom StrataXGS Tomahawk BCM56960 switch controller. It can be installed into Lanner HTCA-6000 Series network appliances to provide 100/40/10GbE fabric connectivity.', 'None', 'Broadcom StrataXGS Tomahawk BCM56960 3.2Tbps bandwidth Multilayer Switch Fabric', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CE Class A, FCC Class A', '-40°C to 70°C', '0°C to 40°C', '5% to 90% (non-condensing)', '283.68 mm x 40 mm x 187.46 mm (11.17', '1 kg (2.2 lbs)', '', '', 23, 'products/HLM-1030_front.png', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6x 100GbE QSFP28, 4x 40GbE QSFP+ and 16x 10GbE SFP+, 2 RJ45 for management and console', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1 x Type A', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
